---
// HeroJournal.astro
---
<section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-32">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
      Unlock Your Mind
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6">
      Journaling<br />Techniques
    </h1> <!-- Yahan galti thi, maine </div> ki jagah </h1> kar diya hai -->
    
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Master the art of journaling to improve clarity, reduce stress, and boost creativity with our daily techniques.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
      <button class="bg-purple-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-purple-700 transition">
        Get Started
      </button>
      <button class="bg-white text-gray-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold border border-gray-300 hover:bg-gray-50 transition">
        Learn More
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>